com.camerontec.catalys.server.adapter

Interface ISharedFixSource

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    JmsSharedConsumer, MQSharedConsumer, SharedFixSourceHelper, SharedSocketAdapter, TIBRVSharedConsumer

    public interface ISharedFixSource
    Objects of this type route messages to different IFIXSource objects based on the the IParty associated with the message.

    • Method Detail

      • fireMessage

        void fireMessage(IFIXMessage message)
          throws MessageException,
                 Exception
        Passes on the given FIX message to be ultimately sent over a FIX session.
        Parameters:
        message - Message to be sent over FIX.
        Throws:
        MessageException - with id of CatalysException.EX_MESSAGE_UnknownParty if there is no FIX source registered for the party associated with this message.
        Exception - If there is a general problem sending the message over FIX.

      • register

        void register(IConnectionPoint connectionPoint,
              IFIXSource fixSource)
        Register a FIX source associated with the given party.

        The fireMessage method will pass messages for this connection point to the given FIX source.

        Parameters:
        connectionPoint - Connection point with which this IFIXSource object is associated.
        fixSource - Source which will receive messages for this party.

      • unregister

        void unregister(IFIXSource fixSource)
        Removes the given source from our listener.
        Parameters:
        fixSource - Source to be removed.

      • getRegisteredSources

        IFIXSource[] getRegisteredSources()
        Returns:
        a list of all the registered IFIXSources.
